                            <li>Provide a competitive advantage in gaining and maintaining access to medicines for patients.</li>
                        </div>
                        <p><strong>Innovation:</strong> A transformation is taking place in the delivery of real world evidence around the world and Pangaea, the new real world evidence portal, is a part of the change at Lilly.</p>
