                            <h2>Mercury</h2>
                            <span>Meeting Management, Contract to Pay and EFPIA Transparency</span>
                        </div>
                        <p><strong>Customer:</strong> Customer Meeting Services.</p>

                        <p><strong>Overview:</strong> Mercury supports Lilly’s newly formed Customer Meeting Services organization through end to end meeting processing. The application enables everything from contracting, to sending invitations, to coordinating honoraria payments and transparency reporting.</p>

                        <p>Mercury empowers Lilly’s ability to report on meeting activities Europe and delivers on the EFPIA required commitments for collection of transparency reporting data starting in 2015.</p>

                        <p><strong>Innovation:</strong> Mercury is a custom-built Force.com app to suit Lilly’s specific CMS needs. It leverages: Force.com, Service Cloud, Heroku, ExactTarget, DocuSign and DrawLoop.</p>
                    </div> 

