                        <p><strong>Overview:</strong> Mission Control facilitates the end to end Cirrus Agile process and is the primary tool used by project teams to perform and manage work when developing applications on the GSO. Mission Control was designed to drive a rigorous approach to manage risks, issues, processes, epics, user stories, test scripts and execution, defects and more while leveraging the collaborative benefits of force.com.</p>

                        <p><strong>Innovation:</strong> A key feature of Mission Control is Chatter, a social capability that enables project teams to collaborate around all aspects of project, specifically project management and the application lifecycle management.</p>
                    </div>
