                        <p><strong>Customer:</strong> IHS – Lilly USA</p>

                        <p><strong>Overview:</strong> MyBusiness gives field staff and office employee’s better line of sight into their territory’s sales and profitability for better management. The application provides multiple data reports integrated into a single reporting solution with actionable insights individualized to each member of the IHS Sales Team.</p>
