                            <h2>SafeStart Stories</h2>
                            <span>Taking Safety Awareness Social</span>
                        </div>
                        <p><strong>Overview:</strong> SafeStart is an advanced safety awareness training program that teaches employees how to recognize and avoid behaviors causing unintentional mistakes and errors not only in the workplace, but also at home and on the road.</p>

                        <p>By encouraging users to share “SafeStart Stories”, story-tellers, listeners and readers relate the principles learned in their training to real-life safety incidents and near-misses. By doing so, they practice the behaviors necessary to reduce the chance of injury.</p>

                        <p><strong>Innovation:</strong> SafeStart Stories utilize integrated social media features such as “liking”, comment threads, and a truly mobile-optimized experience.</p>
                    </div>
