                            <h2>IRISS</h2>
                            <span>Facilitating the Approval of Anti-Corruption Documents</span>
                        </div>
                        <p><strong>Customer:</strong> G&amp;A</p>

                        <p><strong>Overview:</strong> Lilly needed an Ethics and Compliance (E&amp;C) application to track the assessment and approval of local affiliate documents related to Anti-Corruption. Lilly was able to create an application to provide a central repository for Global Policies, Standards and Procedures related to anti-corruption with the intent of managing exceptions and improving adherence at the local, affiliate level.</p>

                        <p>IRISS allows Lilly to:</p>
                        <div class="margin-list">
                            <li>Fill a gap in Reporting, Escalation, and Remediation (RE-3).</li>
                            <li>Submit policy and procedure documents electronically.</li>
                            <li>Provide approval capabilities to document content.</li>
                            <li>Collect and manage Anti-Corruption related documents.</li>
                            <li>Manage assessments performed on locally-developed content.</li>
                            <li>Track intermediate activities and statuses during the review / assessment process.</li>
                        </div>
                    </div>

