                            <h2>Launchpad</h2>
                            <span>A Central Location for all things Cirrus</span>
                        </div>
                        <p><strong>Customer:</strong> Cirrus.</p>

                        <p><strong>Overview:</strong> Launchpad is more than a web page for Cirrus – It’s a portal for ideation, learning, and innovation. Users can submit new project ideas as well as use LaunchPad to lean about Cirrus processes and projects. Additionally, Launchpad provides a gallery of projects that have been delivered on the Force.com platform to help identify potential reuse opportunities.</p>

                        <p>Launchpad streamlined Cirrus’ demand intake process to efficiently get users from project ideation to kickoff. Now, after completing the simple LillyFit Assessment, LaunchPad provides the user with instant feedback about whether or not they are Fit for Force.</p>

                        <p><strong>Innovation:</strong> Launchpad features a custom developed VisualForce page interface that illustrates the capabilities of the Force.com platform to have a custom designed front end powered by the traditional back end of the Force.com platform.</p>
